1
00:01:51,541 --> 00:01:53,333
- Teacher: DON'T FORGET TO
STEER CLEAR OF THE OLD BUILDING

2
00:01:53,416 --> 00:01:55,666
WHEN WALKING TO CLASS TODAY.

3
00:01:55,750 --> 00:01:57,041
THEY'RE KNOCKING IT DOWN SOON,

4
00:01:57,125 --> 00:02:00,208
AND YOU DON'T WANNA BE NEARBY
WHEN IT HAPPENS.

5
00:02:00,291 --> 00:02:01,958
- Nezu: MISS RANMARU!
- SUP?

6
00:02:02,041 --> 00:02:03,541
- DOING ANYTHING AFTER CLASS?

7
00:02:03,625 --> 00:02:05,375
- WE WERE THINKING
OF GOING TO KARAOKE.

8
00:02:05,458 --> 00:02:07,666
YOU SHOULD COME! IT'LL BE
LIKE A WELCOME-BACK PARTY!

9
00:02:07,750 --> 00:02:08,666
OUR TREAT!

10
00:02:08,750 --> 00:02:10,083
- YEAH, I'LL GO
ON ONE CONDITION.

11
00:02:10,166 --> 00:02:12,000
- YOU GOTTA STOP CALLING ME
'MISS RANMARU.'

12
00:02:12,083 --> 00:02:13,083
- Both: OH!

13
00:02:13,166 --> 00:02:14,041
BUT WE THOUGHT
THAT'S WHAT YOU WANTED!

14
00:02:14,125 --> 00:02:15,625
- YEAH, IT'S REALLY NOT.

15
00:02:15,708 --> 00:02:17,500
LADY PANTS! WHY DON'T YOU
COME WITH US?

16
00:02:19,333 --> 00:02:20,708
- I DON'T THINK SO,
MISS RANMARU.

17
00:02:22,291 --> 00:02:23,583
WHY'S EVERYONE
CALLING ME 'MISS?'

18
00:02:23,666 --> 00:02:25,041
IT SOUNDS LIKE YOU'RE
TALKING TO MY MOTHER!

19
00:02:25,125 --> 00:02:26,625
CUT IT OUT AND COME WITH US!
IT'S GONNA BE FUN!

20
00:02:26,708 --> 00:02:28,166
- AT LEAST TELL ME
WHO ELSE IS GONNA BE THERE?

21
00:02:28,250 --> 00:02:30,125
- ME! I'M GONNA
BE THERE! LET'S GO!

22
00:02:30,208 --> 00:02:32,375
ARE YOU READY TO HEAR
THE MOST FEROCIOUS BALLAD EVER?

23
00:02:32,458 --> 00:02:34,416
- YEAH, MY SOUL SISTA!
LET'S ROCK THIS!

24
00:02:34,500 --> 00:02:36,458
...LIKE A CELINE MACHINE!
THANKS FOR INVITING ME.

25
00:02:36,541 --> 00:02:37,791
- WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

26
00:02:37,875 --> 00:02:39,750
- IT'S OKAY IF THESE GUYS
COME WITH US, ISN'T IT?

27
00:02:39,833 --> 00:02:42,166
- I THINK IT'S OKAY
IF MOMIJI COMES.

28
00:02:42,250 --> 00:02:44,041
- YEAH, BUT, I DON'T KNOW
ABOUT ICHIKO.

29
00:02:44,125 --> 00:02:46,125
- WHATEVER. YOU AREN'T
'THOSE GIRLS,' ARE YOU?

30
00:02:46,208 --> 00:02:47,958
- NO, IT'S OKAY.
I DON'T MIND.

31
00:02:48,041 --> 00:02:50,041
THEY WANTED TO THROW YOU
A WELCOME BACK PARTY,

32
00:02:50,125 --> 00:02:52,041
SO GO HAVE A GOOD TIME!

33
00:02:52,125 --> 00:02:53,250
BESIDES, I'M NOT
THAT INTO KARAOKE

34
00:02:53,333 --> 00:02:55,625
AND I'VE GOT LOADS OF OTHER
INVITES TONIGHT!

35
00:02:55,708 --> 00:02:58,958
- AWESOME. YOU HEARD HER. LET'S
GO BEFORE THE ROOMS FILL UP.

36
00:02:59,041 --> 00:03:00,333
- 'KAY. LATER.

37
00:03:00,416 --> 00:03:02,291
- YOUR BAG IS BEGGING FOR
ME TO CARRY IT!

38
00:03:02,375 --> 00:03:04,666
DID I JUST HEAR YOU SAY
YOU DON'T DO KARAOKE?

39
00:03:04,750 --> 00:03:06,541
HOW DOES THAT WORK?

40
00:03:06,625 --> 00:03:08,875
- WHICH SONG WERE YOU
TALKING ABOUT EARLIER?

41
00:03:08,958 --> 00:03:10,625
- AN AWESOME ONE.
- ( Nezu grunting )

42
00:03:10,708 --> 00:03:12,041
- HEY, LET'S GO TO
THE NEW COFFEE SHOP

43
00:03:12,125 --> 00:03:13,625
BY THE TRAIN STATION.

44
00:03:13,708 --> 00:03:14,916
- WE'LL BUY YOU SOME CHOCOLATE!
- DO YOU SEE WHAT SHE'S DOING?

45
00:03:15,000 --> 00:03:16,333
WORKIN' HER TIT-CHIKOS.

46
00:03:22,125 --> 00:03:23,666
- ♪ I SAID NO, I SAID NO, ♪

47
00:03:23,750 --> 00:03:28,125
♪ I SAID NO MATTER HOW MUCH
I THINK OF YOU, OH... ♪

48
00:03:28,208 --> 00:03:30,125
- IT'S LIKE YOU'RE SINGING
INTO MY SOUL.

49
00:03:30,208 --> 00:03:31,791
- CAN I BE YOU WHEN I GROW UP?

50
00:03:31,875 --> 00:03:33,791
- YOU'RE NEXT! DO YOU KNOW
WHAT SONG YOU'RE GONNA SING?

51
00:03:33,875 --> 00:03:35,125
- UH... NO?

52
00:03:35,208 --> 00:03:37,333
- HEY, IS EVERYTHING OKAY?
- YEAH, TOTALLY.

53
00:03:37,416 --> 00:03:38,916
EXCEPT... I DUNNO.

54
00:03:39,000 --> 00:03:40,500
I'M WORRIED ABOUT MISS THANG.

55
00:03:40,583 --> 00:03:43,166
I GOT THE FEELING SHE KINDA
WANTED TO COME WITH US TODAY.

56
00:03:43,250 --> 00:03:44,916
- THEN YOU DON'T
KNOW HER VERY WELL.

57
00:03:45,000 --> 00:03:47,458
- WHEN WE LEFT, SHE WAS
RIGHT WHERE SHE WANTED TO BE.

58
00:03:47,541 --> 00:03:49,583
SURROUNDED BY BOYS
BEGGING TO LICK HER SOCKS!

59
00:03:49,666 --> 00:03:50,791
- I'VE TRIED TO HANG
OUT WITH HER,

60
00:03:50,875 --> 00:03:52,375
BUT SHE ALWAYS SAYS
THE SAME THING.

61
00:03:52,458 --> 00:03:54,333
"I DON'T REALLY CLICK
WITH OTHER GIRLS, SO..."

62
00:03:54,416 --> 00:03:56,500
LIKE I SHOULD'VE KNOWN
AND WAS STUPID FOR ASKING!

63
00:03:56,583 --> 00:03:58,000
- I DON'T KNOW.

64
00:03:58,083 --> 00:04:01,875
EVEN WHEN SHE'S SURROUNDED
BY GUYS SHE SEEMS REALLY LONELY.

65
00:04:01,958 --> 00:04:03,041
- Atsushi: ICHIKO?

66
00:04:03,125 --> 00:04:04,958
ARE WE TALKING
ABOUT THE SAME GIRL?

67
00:04:05,041 --> 00:04:06,375
- THAT WASN'T A
LOOK OF LONELINESS.

68
00:04:06,458 --> 00:04:08,000
THAT WAS A LOOK OF 'OVER IT!'

69
00:04:08,083 --> 00:04:09,666
- ARE YOU REALLY
THAT WORRIED ABOUT ICHIKO?

70
00:04:09,750 --> 00:04:11,208
- I THOUGHT I HAD A GOOD REASON.

71
00:04:11,291 --> 00:04:13,291
- BUT, MAYBE I'M JUST AN IDIOT.
- ( Nakamura singing )

72
00:04:13,375 --> 00:04:15,791
THAT'S WHAT MY MIND SAYS.
BUT MY INSTINCTS DISAGREE.

73
00:04:15,875 --> 00:04:18,041
- THEN WHY DON'T WE GO
OVER THERE AND ASK HER DIRECTLY?

74
00:04:18,125 --> 00:04:19,500
- SHE'S NOT GONNA BE THERE.

75
00:04:19,583 --> 00:04:21,583
SHE SAID SHE HAD
TONS OF OTHER INVITATIONS.

76
00:04:21,666 --> 00:04:22,958
- OH PLEASE.

77
00:04:23,041 --> 00:04:24,583
SHE'S PROBABLY COUNTING
THE FIBERS IN HER THROW RUG.

78
00:04:24,666 --> 00:04:26,666
- LIKE INDIVIDUALLY?

79
00:04:26,750 --> 00:04:30,250
- TWELVE THOUSAND, 206,
12 THOUSAND, 207.

80
00:04:30,333 --> 00:04:31,333
- TOTALLY CALLED IT.

81
00:04:31,416 --> 00:04:32,875
- THIS IS WHAT YOU
DITCHED US TO DO?

82
00:04:32,958 --> 00:04:34,541
- YOU CAN'T BARGE IN WITHOUT
A WARRANT! I COULD ARREST YOU!

83
00:04:34,625 --> 00:04:35,916
- YOU CAN'T ARREST ANYONE!

84
00:04:36,000 --> 00:04:37,791
