WITH ME, SAY SO!

85
00:04:37,875 --> 00:04:39,833
DON'T BE A WUSS AND AVOID ME!

86
00:04:39,916 --> 00:04:40,916
- I SHOULD TAKE THIS
TIME TO POINT OUT

87
00:04:41,000 --> 00:04:42,958
HOW FIERCE MY CANS
LOOK IN THAT TOP!

88
00:04:43,041 --> 00:04:44,958
- I COULDN'T GIVE A CRAP
ABOUT YOUR TOP!

89
00:04:45,041 --> 00:04:47,000
- THAT WAS THE FREAK
WITH THE CHAINSAW, NOT ME!

90
00:04:47,083 --> 00:04:48,916
- STOP! DON'T!
- Ranmaru: CLASSIC DIVA.

91
00:04:49,000 --> 00:04:50,666
- WASN'T THAT FUN? GOOD JOB.

92
00:04:50,750 --> 00:04:52,375
- STOP THAT!

93
00:04:52,458 --> 00:04:54,125
UGH! WHAT DO YOU WANT?

94
00:04:54,208 --> 00:04:55,333
- Both: WE WANT FUN!

95
00:04:55,416 --> 00:04:56,916
- SO WHY DID YOU COME HERE?

96
00:04:57,000 --> 00:04:58,416
- 'CAUSE I WANTED TO HANG
WITH MY FRIEND.

97
00:04:58,500 --> 00:05:00,291
I DON'T HAVE ANYTHING
SPECIFIC IN MIND.

98
00:05:00,375 --> 00:05:02,291
- WHO'S YOUR FRIEND?

99
00:05:02,375 --> 00:05:04,083
- WE CAN WATCH THIS
IF YOU GUYS WANT.

100
00:05:04,166 --> 00:05:06,250
IT'S 'SEVEN SAMURAI.'
I RENTED IT YESTERDAY!

101
00:05:06,333 --> 00:05:07,916
- NO! LET'S WATCH
SOMETHING FUNNY!

102
00:05:08,000 --> 00:05:09,750
- REALLY? DO YOU HAVE
SOMETHING AGAINST NINJAS?

103
00:05:09,833 --> 00:05:11,833
- I JUST THINK NOW WOULD BE
A GOOD TIME TO LAUGH!

104
00:05:11,916 --> 00:05:13,291
- TAKE THAT OUTSIDE!

105
00:05:13,375 --> 00:05:15,375
- YOU HATE MOVIES.
- NO, I DO NOT.

106
00:05:15,458 --> 00:05:19,250
- 'KAY, THEN HOW 'BOUT THIS.
WE, UH, SHOULD, UH...

107
00:05:21,166 --> 00:05:22,125
- LET'S TRASH-TALK OUR EXES!

108
00:05:22,208 --> 00:05:23,500
- I'M NOT TALKING TO
YOU ABOUT THAT!

109
00:05:23,583 --> 00:05:27,916
- YAY, LOVE STORIES...
OR AS THEY SAY... LO-STO!

110
00:05:28,000 --> 00:05:30,166
OUR FIRST STORYTELLER
WILL BE RANMARU.

111
00:05:30,250 --> 00:05:32,125
- NO WAY! RIGHT NOW? OKAY.

112
00:05:32,208 --> 00:05:34,708
SO THERE WAS...
UM, THIS GUY AND...

113
00:05:36,500 --> 00:05:38,291
